# Always Push and Deploy

After finishing user-requested app changes in this project:

1. Commit the relevant changes with a clear message
2. Push to `origin/main`
3. Deploy production with `npx vercel --prod --yes`
4. Return the live production URL

Do this by default without waiting for the user to ask again.
Do not force-push or rewrite published history.
